Total Codes Used
Total number of unique codes referenced in the KNART XML.

Resolved
Number of unique codes used in the KNART XML and present in ontoserver.

Unresolved
Number of unique codes used in the KNART XML and not found in ontoserver.

TSR Requested Codes
Number of unique code system and code pairs referenced in the KNART XML with a placeholder ('TSR-NoCode').

SOLOR Placeholder Codes
Number of unique codes in uuid form referenced in the KNART XML.

Other Unresolved
Number of other unique codes not found in ontoserver, e.g. RXNorm codes.

anf:TSR-NoModel
KAS elements modeled as 'anf:TSR-NoModel' indicates they cannot be modeled in the current version of ANF.
